snippet.title: Best VGM 2084 - Wild Arms 4  - Taste of the Sand that Sheds no Tears
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Wild Arms 4 (2006)
Taste of the Sand that Sheds no Tears
Masato Kouda
